history.content: Sounds like you're trying to push to the 61B repo instead of your own. If you type it "git remote -v" it should display where it's pushing to. If it's not the URL you want, you can do "git remote add origin <url>" if there was no url added previously, or you can do "git remote set-url origin <url>" to change it. After that hopefully you should be able to push! (also make sure you did git init)
